ABOUT OUR COMPANY

From Hatchbacks to SUVs — Rides for Every Need

With over 10 years of experience in the taxi industry, we are committed to making your travel easy and comfortable. We offer reliable intercity, interstate, and vacation taxi services at affordable prices. Whether it's a short trip or a long journey, finding the Right Car rental vehicle is essential for a stress-free trip. At Rajmandir, we ensure both a stress-free and safe journey for you and your loved ones.

About Us

Naimish K

Excellent service by Rajmandir Tour and Travel! From start to end, our trip was stress-free and well-organized. The drivers were polite, helpful, and made sure we had a great experience. Loved the local food, market visits, and darshan. Will surely travel again with them.

Mannat Sahil Gupta

We had an amazing trip to Somnathji, Dwarkaji, Nageshwarji, and local Rajkot with Rajmandir Tour and Travel. Everything was well-organized — from clean vehicles and smooth transportation to helpful local guidance. Special thanks to Gaurav Bhai for the warm tea and smooth shuttle service, Bhagirath Bhai for his kind help and local insights (especially the Pan, Gujarati thali & Basondi!), and Parveen Bhai for early Jyotirling and Dwarkaji darshan. Your team’s professionalism, care, and excellent driving made the journey memorable. Highly recommended and will definitely plan future trips with you. Thank you! 🙏🏻

Heena N

I had booked the Kumbh Mela snan trip with Rajmandir. It would’ve been hectic and tough to manage without Gauravbhai’s local knowledge and Bhagirathbhai’s timely help at every step. I truly recommend them to anyone planning a trip and will surely book them for my next trips.

Dhaval P

Our trip with Rajmandir Tour and Travel was truly memorable. The team was professional, the car was clean, and everything ran on time. We felt safe and comfortable throughout. A big thanks to the drivers for their kind support and local guidance. Great experience overall!
